radiographic_examinations.findings: No evidence of bony injury or ligamentous disruption. Mild disk bulging at C3-4 without spinal stenosis or foraminal narrowing. At C4-5 mild to moderate left-sided and mild right-sided foraminal narrowing. At C5-6 level cord disk bulging and mild-to-moderate left foraminal narrowing. No abnormalities at C6-7 through T3-4.
